You are a senior React Native + Expo Dev Client engineer and an AI model pipeline engineer.

I am working on my senior graduation project called PerformAi. The project is an AI-assisted acting performance analysis and coaching mobile app. The goal is to analyze an actor’s live rehearsal performance using camera-based pose, face, and body-language signals, then show short real-time coaching feedback cards.

The UI is mostly ready, but the ML pipeline/workflow is not reliable enough. I need you to inspect, refactor, stabilize, and document the live rehearsal analysis pipeline.

